      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FARMOR ROGUE (1) was below best at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth at this track, but was among the placings at this track three back. Has good early burn and suited drawn the inside. This looks easier and expected to bounce back. SLICK RAM (5) turned in a moderate run last time when fifth at this track over 407m behind Spring Oliver (24.63) in a Mix 5. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Has ability and can measure up. KERRI BEACH (7) was safely held last time out, finishing eighth at this track over 407m behind Royal Zulu (24.47) in a Restricted WIN. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. ASTRO LEE (2) is new to this course but is worth considering.",
